name: Fish tank (itch) (w24208317)
description:
Room Creator Control:
Press C to get inside of the tank.       Press V to leave the tank

WASD while pressing left mouse button to move camera in first person view

A control panel will show up after joining the room

Need to turn on( red light on ) the control mode button to control the fish manually.

All Fish models are self-made NFTs:
